   319ÔåÆ
   320ÔåÆ	/**
   321ÔåÆ	HTTP headers used to make the request.
   322ÔåÆ
   323ÔåÆ	You can pass a `Headers` instance or a plain object.
   324ÔåÆ
   325ÔåÆ	You can remove a header with `.extend()` by passing the header with an `undefined` value.
   326ÔåÆ
   327ÔåÆ	@example
   328ÔåÆ	```
   329ÔåÆ	import ky from 'ky';
   330ÔåÆ
